@startuml Application Data Workflow

!theme crt-amber

title Application Data - Code Flow and Actions

participant "Application" as app
participant "AppState" as state
participant "Filters" as filters
participant "Logs" as logs
participant "DoubleBuffer" as buffer

== Initialization ==
app -> state: Create AppState
app -> state: DefaultState::Make()
state -> filters: Create default tabs
filters --> state: Tab list ready

== Filter Management ==
app -> state: Add new Filter to Tab
state -> buffer: Get write buffer
buffer --> state: Buffer ready
state -> filters: Create Filter
filters --> state: Filter created
state -> buffer: Write filter to buffer
buffer --> state: Swap buffers

== Condition Management ==
app -> state: Add Condition to Filter
state -> filters: Condition data
filters --> state: Condition created

== Active Flags ==
app -> state: SetFlag(IsActive) on Filter
state -> filters: Update filter status
filters --> state: Status updated

== Layer Visibility ==
app -> state: SetLayerActive(logs_view, true)
state --> app: Layer state updated

== Search Operation ==
app -> state: Search for log index
state -> logs: Update SearchedLog
logs --> state: Index found/not found

== Get Visible Logs ==
app -> state: GetVisibleChunk()
state -> buffer: Get read buffer
buffer --> state: Current chunk
state --> app: Return VisibleLogsChunk

== Plugin Integration ==
app -> state: GetIFluxionLogsPlugin()
state --> app: IFluxionLogsPlugin*
app -> state: Apply filters via plugin
state -> filters: Get active filters
filters --> state: Filter vector
app -> state: Update visible chunk
state -> logs: VisibleLogsChunk updated

@enduml
